  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Clicking the login link (the one in the header) from any page results in this use case.

Not sure if this is a bug.

The login links within the git mission have the correct redirects to send the user back to the 
mission (and tested, work for Google and user acct login)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg3045">msg3045 (view)</a></th>
   <th>Author: annalee</th>
   <th>Date: 2012-02-25.20:25:56</th>
