  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>From <a href="https://openhatch.org/missions/git,">https://openhatch.org/missions/git,</a> when you hit the login link and log in
using Google, a successful login redirects you to
<a href="http://openhatch.org/account/login/,">http://openhatch.org/account/login/,</a> instead of back to
<a href="https://openhatch.org/missions/git.">https://openhatch.org/missions/git.</a>

Hitting "log out" likewise redirects to home.

Not tested: any login methods other than Google.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
